    <string name="SectionOneTheoryPropsAnswerThree_3">-12</string>
    <string name="SectionOneTheoryPropsCorrectAnswer_3">81</string>


    <string name="SectionOneTheoryWorkedExamples_3">Estimate √10 to one decimal place.\n
Step 1: 3² = 9 &lt; 10 &lt; 16 = 4², so 3 &lt; √10 &lt; 4.\n
Step 2: Try 3.1²= 9.61 &lt; 10 and 3.2² = 10.24 &gt; 10.\n
Step 3: So 3.1 &lt; √10 &lt; 3.2.\n
Step 4: Try 3.16² = 9.9856 ≈ 10, so √10 ≈ 3.2.</string>
