    <string name="SectionSevenTheoryWorkedExamples_3">Simplify ⁴√(81x⁸).\n
Step 1: Write as: ⁴√81 · ⁴√x⁸.\n
Step 2: ⁴√81 = ⁴√3⁴ = 3.\n
Step 3: ⁴√x⁸ = x⁸/⁴ = x².\n
Step 4: Result: 3x².</string>
