    <string name="SectionEightTheoryDef_3">• For a > 0 and x = p/q, aˣ = a^(p/q) = ⁹√aᵖ.\n
• If a = 0 and x > 0, then aˣ = 0.\n
• Extends powers to rational exponents.</string>
